{"tid":2068300,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今年係咪冇乜人畢業？","createTime":"2020-06-17T14:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T15:39:18.000Z","uid":113337,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e056850b3083a2f6d80b5cc23a1a0503ace4d4b","tid":2068300,"uid":113337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"其實今年係咪無乜人畢業？<br />\n情願選擇defer 下年畢業<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係邊會咁靜，無人講FG搵唔到工？<br />\n留意下請人既網都發現，公司少左好多請人對比上年。<br />\n但好撚多果堆乜撚野wealth management trainee 好撚煩，成個網5，6頁都係依堆野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定係個個FG搵到工50k....？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb1738a6084dadf939aab3b06713044701d7052","tid":2068300,"uid":118127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"大把人grad，我我公司都大把fg"},{"pid":"77a01255ff656609b4d3d8a19aa6ed0c51dcc772","tid":2068300,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"b3ad77e9805e1f827b1b7edc42a50e9f039b09d0","tid":2068300,"uid":77319,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"2020 fg 未搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd60291d6d6acaaf7530e2743e10b1da1042f1f2","tid":2068300,"uid":90304,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cd97654f73ee4191dfd9a9e5c75d418171bc0f","tid":2068300,"uid":341791,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"好難突然defer<br />\n又無理由為左defer特登肥佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae51ccb2049fb51c0f1b90f56b9706303ee9f7f","tid":2068300,"uid":113337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"39cd97654f73ee4191dfd9a9e5c75d418171bc0f","tid":2068300,"uid":341791,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"好難突然defer<br />\n又無理由為左defer特登肥佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:05:21.000Z","msg":"真係有人突登Defer，聽講過Drop曬科。或者hea讀炒左去...."},{"pid":"e8f1122cbc9f9bb3a64f031741515d90a12a4772","tid":2068300,"uid":349002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae51ccb2049fb51c0f1b90f56b9706303ee9f7f","tid":2068300,"uid":113337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"39cd97654f73ee4191dfd9a9e5c75d418171bc0f","tid":2068300,"uid":341791,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"好難突然defer<br />\n又無理由為左defer特登肥佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\